Comment: Simple enough to be done in less that 5 minutes yet entertaining.

I've always been curious why a contribution is uploaded twice. Do you have any idea? I'd like to report the issue to CG some time.

(In your case, the other link is:
https://www.codingame.com/contribute/view/58821f056f7ab1f1f6b7550b2ecb7df308944 )

Thanks.

Uploading two times is good for my stats - but since you caught me I will delete the other one.

I think it is due to internet connectivity. My connection was bad during uploading. When a contribution already exists and I am editing it, a bad connection results in an error message (something like 'you are not in the latest version of this contribution'). However, when the contribution does not yet exist (uploading for the first time), a bad connection can simply result in multiple new contributions.

Thanks! I think one of the comments I've typed the most (to many different players, not just you) is that "Your contribution has been uploaded twice. Please remove one of them". So many times that I always wonder why and how it can be fixed. So, thank you for your input and I'll try to follow it up if I can. :)
